Daniel WARREN, Appellant
v.
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ATTORNEY GENERAL, Appellee No. 31 MAP 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Decided: February 20, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM

AND NOW, this 20 th day of February, 2019, the order of the Commonwealth Court is AFFIRMED . Appellant's ancillary request for relief, filed on November 27, 2018, is DENIED as moot.
